-ui-labelWidget'>Azerbaijani</label><div lang='az' dir='ltr' class='wbmi-caption-value'>Nikola Teslanın portreti, təxminən 1890-cı il.</div></div><div style='display:none;' class='wbmi-entityview-caption wbmi-entityview-hideable oo-ui-layout oo-ui-horizontalLayout'><label class='wbmi-language-label oo-ui-widget oo-ui-widget-enabled oo-ui-labelElement-label oo-ui-labelElement oo-ui-labelWidget'>Russian</label><div lang='ru' dir='ltr' class='wbmi-caption-value'>Портрет Николы Теслы, около 1890 года.</div></div><div style='display:none;' class='wbmi-entityview-caption wbmi-entityview-hideable oo-ui-layout oo-ui-horizontalLayout'><label class='wbmi-language-label oo-ui-widget oo-ui-widget-enabled oo-ui-labelElement-label oo-ui-labelElement oo-ui-labelWidget'>Arabic</label><div lang='ar' dir='rtl' class='wbmi-caption-value'>صورة لنيكولا تيسلا ، حوالي عام 1890.</div></div><div style='display:none;' class='wbmi-entityview-caption wbmi-entityview-hideable oo-ui-layout oo-ui-horizontalLayout'><label class='wbmi-language-label oo-ui-widget oo-ui-widget-enabled oo-ui-labelElement-label oo-ui-labelElement oo-ui-labelWidget'>German</label><div lang='de' dir='ltr' class='wbmi-caption-value'>Porträt von Nikola Tesla, um 1890.</div></div><div style='display:none;' class='wbmi-entityview-caption wbmi-entityview-hideable oo-ui-layout oo-ui-horizontalLayout'><label class='wbmi-language-label oo-ui-widget oo-ui-widget-enabled oo-ui-labelElement-label oo-ui-labelElement oo-ui-labelWidget'>French</label><div lang='fr' dir='ltr' class='wbmi-caption-value'>Portrait de Nikola Tesla, vers 1890.</div></div><div style='display:none;' class='wbmi-entityview-caption wbmi-entityview-hideable oo-ui-layout oo-ui-horizontalLayout'><label class='wbmi-language-label oo-ui-widget oo-ui-widget-enabled oo-ui-labelElement-label oo-ui-labelElement oo-ui-labelWidget'>Burmese</label><div lang='my' dir='ltr' class='wbmi-caption-value'>မြန်မာဘာသာ</div></div><div style='display:none;' class='wbmi-entityview-caption wbmi-entityview-hideable oo-ui-layout oo-ui-horizontalLayout'><label class='wbmi-language-label oo-ui-widget oo-ui-widget-enabled oo-ui-labelElement-label oo-ui-labelElement oo-ui-labelWidget'>Marathi</label><div lang='mr' dir='ltr' class='wbmi-caption-value'>निकोल tesla</div></div><div style='display:none;' class='wbmi-entityview-caption wbmi-entityview-hideable oo-ui-layout oo-ui-horizontalLayout'><label class='wbmi-language-label oo-ui-widget oo-ui-widget-enabled oo-ui-labelElement-label oo-ui-labelElement oo-ui-labelWidget'>Portuguese</label><div lang='pt' dir='ltr' class='wbmi-caption-value'>Fórmula JPX Cálculo da Força e Velocidade  Usando as leis de: energia cinética, segunda lei de Newton,velocidade por aceleração.Cheguei àconclusão de que podemos calcular a potência explosiva do motor,então podemos usar:V= I² / 2.P Criador:João p(eu)</div></div><div style='display:none;' class='wbmi-entityview-caption wbmi-entityview-hideable oo-ui-layout oo-ui-horizontalLayout'><label class='wbmi-language-label oo-ui-widget oo-ui-widget-enabled oo-ui-labelElement-label oo-ui-labelElement oo-ui-labelWidget'>Spanish</label><div lang='es' dir='ltr' class='wbmi-caption-value'>Una imagen fotográfica de Nikola Tesla [1856-1943] a los 34 años.</div></div><div style='display:none;' class='wbmi-entityview-caption wbmi-entityview-hideable oo-ui-layout oo-ui-horizontalLayout'><label class='wbmi-language-label oo-ui-widget oo-ui-widget-enabled oo-ui-labelElement-label oo-ui-labelElement oo-ui-labelWidget'>Brazilian Portuguese</label><div lang='pt-br' dir='ltr' class='wbmi-caption-value'>Uma imagem fotográfica de Nikola Tesla (1856-1943) aos 34 anos, por volta de 1890 tirada por Napoleon Sarony (1821–1896).</div></div><div style='display:none;' class='wbmi-entityview-caption wbmi-entityview-hideable oo-ui-layout oo-ui-horizontalLayout'><label class='wbmi-language-label oo-ui-widget oo-ui-widget-enabled oo-ui-labelElement-label oo-ui-labelElement oo-ui-labelWidget'>Persian</label><